<Overview3Cols>
    <Text1>
        <strong>System Report</strong> generates comprehensive reports on Proxmox VE infrastructure, providing detailed analysis of clusters, nodes, virtual machines, and storage resources.<br />
        It creates structured documentation for compliance, auditing, and capacity planning purposes.<br />
        The module captures configuration details, resource utilization, and system specifications to support informed decision-making.
    </Text1>
    <Text2>
        <strong>Infrastructure Documentation</strong>: Creates detailed reports for compliance audits and system documentation.<br />
        <strong>Capacity Planning</strong>: Provides resource utilization data to support growth and optimization decisions.<br />
        <strong>Configuration Analysis</strong>: Documents system configurations, VM specifications, and storage allocations.<br />
        <strong>Export Capabilities</strong>: Generates reports in multiple formats for sharing and archival purposes.<br />
    </Text2>
    <Text3>
        <strong>Seamless Integration</strong>: Works natively with Proxmox VE to collect accurate system information.<br />
        <strong>Comprehensive Coverage</strong>: Analyzes all aspects of the virtualization infrastructure in a single report.<br />
        <strong>Professional Output</strong>: Generates well-formatted reports suitable for management and stakeholder presentations.<br />
    </Text3>
</Overview3Cols>
